 * Essay Layout Example — Kitchen sink demonstrating every slide type.
 * Visit /essays/example to see all layouts with labels.
 *
 * This page reuses a subset of the Nomads photo set for demonstration.
 * Each slide is labeled with its component name and key props.
 */
